1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:05,200
Nothing escapes a black hole — except the truth about how they work.

2
00:00:05,200 --> 00:00:10,800
Black holes are regions where gravity is so strong, not even light can escape.

3
00:00:10,800 --> 00:00:17,200
They form when massive stars collapse, creating an event horizon — the point of no return.

4
00:00:17,200 --> 00:00:20,000
Inside, gravity distorts spacetime, creating bizarre effects.

5
00:00:20,000 --> 00:00:21,600
Imagine time slowing down.

6
00:00:21,600 --> 00:00:28,400
So, while we can't escape a black hole, understanding them reveals the true wonders of the universe.

7
00:00:28,400 --> 00:00:30,400
Curious for more cosmic mysteries?

8
00:00:30,400 --> 00:00:32,000
Hit that follow button!
